[18.3511, "o", "Based on my exploration of the codebase, here"]
[18.40594, "o", "'s what I know:\r\n\r\n## About the Project ("]
[18.481326, "o", "Pawan)\r\n\r\n**Pawan** (Sanskrit for"]
[18.555536, "o", " \"wind\") is a Rust-based AI coding agent workspace"]
[18.617332, "o", " with:\r\n\r\n- **pawan-core**: Library crate"]
[18.691334, "o", " (`pawan`) providing the agent engine, tools"]
[18.766497, "o", ", config, and self-healing capabilities\r\n- **"]
[18.829737, "o", "pawan-cli**: Binary with Clap CLI"]
[18.890999, "o", " and Ratatui TUI interface\r\n- **"]
[18.965842, "o", "pawan-mcp**: Model Context Protocol support ("]
[19.041598, "o", "daedra server)\r\n- **pawan-a"]
[19.10365, "o", "egis** & **pawan-web**: Additional"]
[19.179615, "o", " components\r\n\r\n**Key Architecture:**\r\n- `agent"]
[19.244572, "o", "::backend::LlmBackend` trait abstracts"]
[19.304146, "o", " LLM providers\r\n- Implementations: `Open"]
[19.366887, "o", "AiCompatBackend` (NVIDIA NIM"]
[19.441025, "o", ", OpenAI, DeepSeek, MLX) and"]
[19.504457, "o", " `OllamaBackend` (local)\r\n"]
[19.566906, "o", "- `tools::Tool` trait + `Tool"]
[19.641047, "o", "Registry` for tool registration\r\n- Config from `p"]
[19.713825, "o", "awan.toml` in project root\r\n- E"]
[19.777582, "o", "ruka bridge for 3-tier memory injection\r\n"]
[19.84121, "o", "- Cloud fallback support for hybrid routing\r\n-"]
[19.915245, "o", " Self-healing with error fixing, test editing, auto"]
[20.002331, "o", "-commit"]
[20.002891, "o", "\r\n"]
[20.003025, "o", "\r\n**Default Setup:**\r\n- Provider:"]
[20.064226, "o", " NVIDIA NIM (`https://integrate.api.n"]
[20.139874, "o", "vidia.com/v1`)\r\n- API key from `N"]
[20.202975, "o", "VIDIA_API_KEY` env (auto-loaded via dot"]
[20.26727, "o", "envy)\r\n- Model: `mistralai"]
[20.327529, "o", "/mistral-small-4-119b-"]
[20.390027, "o", "2603`\r\n- Features: TUI enabled by"]
[20.468149, "o", " default, MCP support\r\n\r\n## About the User\r\n\r\n"]
[20.557732, "o", "- **Git author**: bkataru <baalate"]
[20.621916, "o", "ja.k@gmail.com>\r\n- **Workspace author"]
[20.687513, "o", "**: Dirmacs <build@dirmacs"]
[20.752329, "o", ".com>\r\n- **Repository**: https://github.com"]
[20.841564, "o", "/dirmacs/pawan\r\n- Current configuration uses"]
[20.9189, "o", " NVIDIA cloud with local Ollama paused (swap-bound)"]
[20.942855, "o", "\r\n\r\n--- 17 iterations, 15 tool calls, 117665 tokens (think:975 act:1361) ---\r\n  [ok] bash (10ms)\r\n  [ok] bash (6ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (1ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (1ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] bash (5ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] bash (6ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (0ms)\r\n  [ok] read_file (1ms)\r\n"]
